### 测试用户登录
POST http://localhost:8081/user/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "testuser",
  "password": "123456"
}

### 测试错误密码
POST http://localhost:8081/user/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "testuser",
  "password": "wrongpassword"
}

### 测试不存在的账号
POST http://localhost:8081/user/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "nonexistent",
  "password": "123456"
}

### 获取用户列表
GET http://localhost:8081/user/list

### 测试用户注册
POST http://localhost:8081/user/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "newuser",
  "password": "123456",
  "nickname": "新用户"
}

### 测试注册已存在的账号
POST http://localhost:8081/user/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "testuser",
  "password": "123456",
  "nickname": "重复注册"
}

### 测试用户注册（新同学）
POST http://localhost:8081/user/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "newstudent01",
  "password": "888",
  "nickname": "大四闲置出清"
}
